Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,------------Text------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愛子?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是她原來的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}根據愛子同學生前的人際關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最後找到了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒有辦法救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自那以來已經好久沒見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小柳小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還以為她會過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是說不想和我們扯上關係了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看來被討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倒不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找我們有什麼事 修一同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把你們隊伍收集到的硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全部交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們無法與別人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}應該把之後的事交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後回歸普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望你們給個令人滿意的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我現在依然認為你是個溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝你在那座山上保護了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然只有那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}與你合為一體的那段經歷我是不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不跟她說點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和她已經不是一個世界的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒有資格再接受別人的謝意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那傢伙的表情變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是就這麼留下他不管的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉岡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳的判斷是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們明天翹課去山裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不像是優等生會說的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有話直說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不我們去租一部電影看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在你家裡 就我們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後等天亮了再去山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我就直接回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相對地 我們的關係也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}僅僅維持了一個夏天的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把迄今為止發生的一切全部忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}做回素不相識的兩個人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們是不可分離的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就由我來保護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}幫助我走到最後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可不打算一味地接受你的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一變了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改變他的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且再繼續這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們是無法真正合為一體的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有些事需要確認
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}稍微等一下 我馬上就收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這種東西怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}加上之前發現的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一果然有點不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}進來吧 紅愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一 這個房子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖說窄了點 還請妳隨意一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那邊的沙發可以坐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喔 不用擔心我的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}畢竟他們都有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}究竟怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一看不到這個房間的現狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你說你父母每天都忙到很晚來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 平常我都是吃完晚餐就直接上二樓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從小時候開始就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一 你好好回想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你最後一次見到父母是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最後一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}絕對沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這肯定是江麗奈的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一沒有喝下藥物的那段記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個女人可以隨意篡改別人的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道…不只是我們的父母…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就連修一的父母…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起 修一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是因為與我們姐妹扯上了關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紅…愛?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想做什麼都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是加賀谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我把能力解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣一來我們就毫無瓜葛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天下午五點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}來商場的停車場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會把我們收集到的硬幣全部給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們兩人務必一同前來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣可以了吧 吉岡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 謝謝妳 小柳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}加上修一同學 我們不應該繼續收集硬幣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們得把硬幣都轉交給江麗奈小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要儘快結束這場遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這才是上策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江麗奈說什麼時候見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天下午五點 在城裡的河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉岡人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒看見她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像是請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他們肯定有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不想回答的話也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是你從昨晚開始就一直怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我自己也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等我想清楚了會告訴妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是以前的江麗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼她會在我家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個情形 她彷彿是在保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會盯著那傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這不是妳的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們無法阻止愛子的同學被抹除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我對她進行和對修一同學一樣的處理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少她也許能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒有這樣做 是為了愛子同學的復仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果妳那樣做了 妳的能力會減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們打倒那傢伙的勝算也就會降低
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有別的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一還是老樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 他在那時用槍指向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他應該還沒有回想起與我們的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果讓那傢伙再次察覺到修一的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}靠著這份聯繫回想起一切的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那時…世界將會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請在截止日期前提交相關材料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就快要離開這城市了 感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然還有半年才畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還是會感覺有些孤零零吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我試試用氣味去找吉岡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被妳盯著怪不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看來妳這手機不防水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聯繫不上小柳真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}給妳一個忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳整天板著個臉 但其實付出了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有時候故意拉開一些距離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳才會收穫更多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混蛋女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我這邊解決了 我們在哪裡會合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 硬幣是絕對不會交給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿勇…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別叫得那麼親密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到此為止吧 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你本身就不適合戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉岡會去河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}畢業之後就要分離了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}河邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完了 可能趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一同學在那之後怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳指的是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是妳對他說了什麼多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到時候妳也就別想活命了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江麗奈小姐 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為了保護我 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一同學 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳走吧 這裡沒妳事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剛剛她交給妳的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是硬幣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然不肯回答我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是今天我也不打算中途收手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}停一下 到這裡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝 但是妳為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別管那麼多 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然不知道是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是修一同學一定在等著妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}畢竟我也一直在關注著他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨晚 我終於回想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我獲得力量之前的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然只有一點點片段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我迄今為止的想法都錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是妳把我捲了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恐怕是我讓妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聽不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怕不是想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這些事我也很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紅愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 我去調查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一 有一些過去的聯繫 你多半是忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們記得這個東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一同學 不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要再繼續回憶下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不會再讓妳奪取我的記憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個交給妳了 妳快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我被妳的善良保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}同時也被束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一直接觸不到事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從昨晚開始 我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:16:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫非那也是在用某種手段保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也明白自己的做法有些過分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不打算辯解什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那時我就已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起 修一同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忘掉你的力量 忘掉這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像個普通人一樣活著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之後就交給我和直人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和記憶當中一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從妳身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我聞到了和紅愛一模一樣的哀傷的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以不用再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們不必再獨自背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是個空殼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過 正因為是空殼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才能像這樣和我融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才能給我一個歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自從進入到你空空的身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的內心也終於不再空虛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們上吧 紅愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳這個賤女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}穗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那已經是和她截然不同的其他生物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這都是些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江麗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那再怎麼問你也是白費力氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能夠吸引我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有人與人之間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要不來那個地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怪物什麼的 我不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個地方說的是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剛剛那個難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宇宙飛船的墜落地點…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們沒必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這之前我和外星人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要趕在所有人之前集齊一百枚硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要和紅愛一起結束這場遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還要背負起連累妳犯下的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一定是為此自己選擇這種力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別太自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓這場遊戲結束的 會是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直都能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在在這個城市的暗處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龐大的故事正徐徐展開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我大概並不是這個故事的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我或許應該退出故事的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回歸到普通人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有段日子不見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們兩個的精神狀態好了許多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼咱們就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去你們說的那個墜落地點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當這個故事在某一天迎來結尾的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若是我們兩個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也許能找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就堅信這一點繼續前進吧
